snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Corrupted Twilight Sparkle, Dusk Till Dawn (Come Learn With Pibby x FNF Mod)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' Corrupted Twilight Sparkle | Dusk Till Dawn (FULL WEEK DEMO) for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD. Pinkie Pie and BF must take down the corruption as a team.
Jakeneutron - Mod Creator: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9-6l_kAn1rg
 
This is the official Dusk Till Dawn, I know a bunch of Dusk Till Dawn fanmade were made but it's not what I'm playing. It's actually the official version that just got released last night. There are some secrets this time and a new game over animation. I couldn’t really figure out what the secret meant so you gonna have to download it and help solve the secret, I think by solving the secret it could help BFand Pibby stop the corruption from taking over fnf mods.

Dusk Till Dawn (Come Learn With Pibby x FNF Mod)
Download Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/FNFsPDuskTillDawn/693307

Game Note by Jakeneutron: It's finally here! Dusk Till Dawn, the first official Jakeneutron Pibby mod is now out and playable! This mod includes an Easy, Normal, and Hard chart! But there's a secret for beating Hard.

We'll be playing Dusk Till Dawn on very hard, the mod has 1 song, 1 new game over screen and secrets. Will Boyfriend get corrupted or will BF be able to survive this corrupted world and save Girlfriend/GF? Let's find out!

Dusk Till Dawn Secret Phase 2
https://youtu.be/pi42370fSnU
Dusk Till Dawn Secret Phase 3
https://youtu.be/DzITRjXcCZM
